Package: ats-proxy-enterprise
Version: 3.0-beta-1
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ats-core (>= 9.2.13), ats-proxy-plugin (>= 3.0-beta), ats-proxy-hardening (>= 3.0-beta)
Maintainer: ATS Proxy Enterprise <proxy@tripersonale.org>
Homepage: https://github.com/tripersonale/ats-proxy-enterprise
Description: ATS Proxy Enterprise v3.0 — forward proxy with filtering, auth and hardening
 Meta-package that installs ats-core, ats-proxy-plugin, and ats-proxy-hardening.
 Provides a complete forward proxy with URL filtering, Basic Auth, and 25-point
 hardening profile. One command for the full stack.
